comments: Agbaji (UTA) delivers body contact to Williams (BOS) and affects Williams' (BOS) SQBR during the drive. The illegal contact occurs prior to Williams' gather and a personal foul is correctly assessed.
Kornet (BOS) establishes himself in Kessler's (UTA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
All Flagrant Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Williams (BOS) legally contests Agbaji's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Both Horton-Tucker (UTA) and Brown (BOS) engage and then disengage in incidental contact as Brown is cutting through the lane.
Olynyk (UTA) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Olynyk (UTA) establishes himself in Brogdon's (BOS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Kessler (UTA) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Kessler (UTA) establishes himself in Brogdon's (BOS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Williams (BOS) absorbs the marginal body that occurs during Horton-Tucker's (UTA) driving shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) initiates body contact with Horton-Tucker (UTA) that affects his ability to gather the ball at the end of his drive.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Horton-Tucker (UTA) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Kessler (UTA) avoids making contact to Williams' (BOS) arm, and cleanly blocks the play at the basket.
